 9. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
10. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
11. the person eating zucchini is the person traveling to marseilles##1
12. the person eating cranberry is the person traveling to hamburg##1
13. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
14. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
15. the person eating zucchini is on the far right##1
16. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
17. the person drinking lemonade is the person traveling to marseilles##1
18. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far right##1
19. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
20. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
